                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>Trunk no longer has support for hadoop1.  You cannot build against hadoop1.  We now generate one artifact only and our artifact naming no longer includes the hadoop version we were built against since we only build against one version, hadoop2: e.g. the hbase 1.0.0 release will be named hbase-1.0.0, not hbase-1.0.0-hadoop1 (or hbase-1.0.0-hadoop2).</customfieldvalue>

